<li id="cite_note-IEP-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-IEP_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-IEP_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Grattan-Guinness, Ivor and Walsh, Alison (2008), "Benjamin Peirce", <i>Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy</i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/peirce-benjamin/">Eprint</a>.</span></li>
